title: Honduras beats Haiti 1-0 in Olympic qualifying opener
text:
Published By: Fox News: Sports - Today 
CARSON, Calif. (AP) Antony Lozano scored in the sixth minute and Honduras held on to beat Haiti 1-0 on Friday night in their Group B opener ...
